# Motion Standards

Motion should feel like silk fabric.

Never abrupt.

## Luxury Easing

cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1)

## Fade Easing

cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)

## Rules

Animate only:

- opacity
- transform

Never animate:

- width
- height
- left
- top
- margin
- padding

## Framer Motion

Always:

viewport={{ once: true }}

Avoid:

- Infinite loops
- Repeated viewport triggers
- Excessive spring physics

## Scroll Reveals

Preferred:

- Text fade-up
- Character reveals
- Subtle parallax
- Image scale reveal

Avoid flashy effects.
